[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    160[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - Risk tier thresholds are externalized with operational context (nurse capacity, outreach cadence). A reader understands these are business decisions, not model outputs.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    161[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - The `evaluate_model` function focuses on metrics that matter clinically (precision at threshold, tier distribution) rather than just academic metrics (accuracy).
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    162[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - DynamoDB TTL pattern correctly auto-expires stale predictions after the prediction window.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    163[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - The filtering of LOW risk patients before DynamoDB write is a smart operational choice, well-explained.
